princeton_ansible.title: Ruby role succeeds even if ruby version used is wrong

comments.body:
On the machines in question, rvm was installed. I did `sudo rvm implode` and `sudo rm /etc/rvmrc`, then re-ran the ansible playbook.

It would be good to have this role ensure that the correct version of ruby is running according to `ruby -v`
